<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Buzón Ciudadano</h1>
    <p>Hola <%= @responsible_person.name %>,</p>
    <p>Te informamos que la sugerencia "<%= @suggestion.title %>" se ha cerrado por inactividad.</p>
    <p>A partir de este momento solo se permite comentar a los responsables del ayuntamiento.<p>
    <p><%= link_to 'Ir a la sugerencia', @url %></p>
    <p>Gracias por utilizar el Buzón Ciudadano</p>
    <br>
    <p>--------------------------------------------------------------</p>
    <br>
    <h1>Suggestion Box</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= @responsible_person.name %>,</p>
    <p>We inform you that the suggestion "<%= @suggestion.title %>" was closed for inactivity.</p>
    <p>From now only allowed to publish new comments to the city council responsible people.<p>
    <p><%= link_to 'Go to suggestion', @url %></p>
    <p>Thank you for using the Suggestion Box</p>
  </body>
</html>
